Incident Response Runbook Flow. Five steps: 1) Detect (Metrics/Alerts: Cost Spike, Error Rate, Quality Drop) -> 2) Triage (Provider vs System? All Users vs Group?) -> 3) Mitigate (Fallback Model, Clear Cache, Rollback Prompt) -> 4) Resolve (Root Cause, Fix, Deploy) -> 5) Learn (Update Runbook, Sharpen Metrics, Post-Mortem). Boxes with arrows, decision diamonds. Hotline icon for Safety incidents. German labels.